{"tid":1875338,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"我婆打黎問屋企條屎渠會唔會有事","createTime":"2020-02-11T17:21:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T17:30:48.000Z","uid":212944,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d941471f7f4bcca6b9d8f97e94e55ff81c277b0d","tid":1875338,"uid":212944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T17:21:52.000Z","msg":"我婆打黎問屋企條屎渠會唔會有事，我能想到最layman 的方法解釋，就係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">條屎渠其實會放屁，青衣的屎渠就是剛巧在屋裡放了一個「可能有病毒」的屁。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\nSARS讓我們對屎渠又敬又畏，隱約知道了有個U位，知其又不知其所以然，其實本來就是用水來防止病毒臭氣昆蟲入屋，淘大E座就是因為U位沒水，失靈了，才出了大事。<br />\n<br />\n昨晚袁教授說的排氣喉（vent pipe）則是另一件事。ladies and gentlemen，接受吧，屎渠是會放屁的。閣下的屎就如在腸道中一般在屎渠發酵，繼而放屁，如果沒有排氣喉，那些屁就會不時從閣下的屎塔裡噴出屁的泡泡，所以<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屎渠是必然跟著一條屁渠</span></span></strong>(for your easier understanding)的，而這條屁喉的頂部是疏氣的，而臭屁唔響，它一直都在天台放著很臭的屁。<br />\n<br />\n放屁很正常，問題是屁放了在家裡。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">每個屎塔都會有一個分支在U位後接通屁喉的連接位</span></span></strong>（反虹吸管，anti siphonage pipe），現在其實還沒有確實的官方原因，但somehow就是這個位漏氣了，本來該放在外的屁放了在屋裡了，病毒 *有可能* 這樣傳開了。<br />\n<br />\n我解釋到這裡我婆直接地問，咁即係我間屋有無事，我說，跟公樓私樓無關係，淘大夠私樓啦，我婆又直接再問我最近有無起過啲乜野樓，我話，都有既，一個公廁囉，她突然謹慎，沒再說話，我補充條渠其實唔係我畫既，但似乎沒有說服力。<br />\n<br />\nwell，防疫之本係少出街，少出街，又用少個口罩，又唔會去到我個公廁，多謝收睇。<br />\n<br />\n**編按：所以，沖廁就放下廁板吧，如果唔係你覺得塊廁板要黎做乜，俾你當凳坐？<br />\n<br />\n#放屁傳唔傳染<br />\n#專家點睇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s960x960/84351186_10162925849160623_6640962043203551232_o.jpg?_nc_cat=108&amp;_nc_ohc=qfMrKYYcDVQAX8seyDW&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-1.xx&amp;oh=e39814ac632368e68a7bc872da6f2356&amp;oe=5EB597C1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fs960x960%2F84351186_10162925849160623_6640962043203551232_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D108%26_nc_ohc%3DqfMrKYYcDVQAX8seyDW%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-1.xx%26oh%3De39814ac632368e68a7bc872da6f2356%26oe%3D5EB597C1&h=f42c5622&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10162925849150623&amp;set=a.10150560677520623&amp;type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D10162925849150623%26set%3Da.10150560677520623%26type%3D3%26theater&d=k4A9UPuxEtmwSexvyTVA%2BUwAUq3ZsepC89uAf1Ef2WI%3D&h=414f98e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10162925849150623&amp;set=a.10150560677520623&amp;type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n利申：純粹係facebook見到覺得好正又好易明，所以係到轉發<br />\n我唔是原po樓主"},{"pid":"e5118dc3afb43194c511b28a1a32a4d0985112ef","tid":1875338,"uid":212944,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T17:23:14.000Z","msg":"琴晚聽完個記者會完全唔明<br />\n睇完原po即刻明晒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cea88c8f1aadb0bb1b64bc678b19bc9bacfeabe3","tid":1875338,"uid":212944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T17:24:50.000Z","msg":"見到呢句笑到仆街<br />\n<blockquote>SARS讓我們對屎渠又敬又畏，隱約知道了有個U位，知其又不知其所以然</blockquote>"},{"pid":"a199f5f1789662f34779809f0a0e1fc90b629a3f","tid":1875338,"uid":50270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5118dc3afb43194c511b28a1a32a4d0985112ef","tid":1875338,"uid":212944,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T17:23:14.000Z","msg":"琴晚聽完個記者會完全唔明<br />\n睇完原po即刻明晒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T17:24:51.000Z","msg":"你咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af45a94b909bf1ad432f959e1dec20a9d8b86542","tid":1875338,"uid":212944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s